curam.util.persistence

Class EntityInfo<I,E extends Entity<I>,S extends DeepCloneable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.persistence.EntityInfo<I,E,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - The identifier type used by the physical database table which "seeds" the entity instance.
    E - The type of the logical entity.
    S - The generated "dtls" struct corresponding to the physical database table which "seeds" the entity instance.

    public class EntityInfo<I,E extends Entity<I>,S extends DeepCloneable>
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable convenience object which contains all the information for managing an instance of a logical entity.
